    {
        "content": "<p>macovedj <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13891#issuecomment-5006627411\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13891\">PR #13891</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Thanks for this! I believe this is correct but I'd ideally like to refactor things to avoid duplication to prevent something like this cropping up in the future, so I'm curious on your thoughts on the below</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Yep that concern makes sense to me.  I just had a go at extracting it out.  I'm pretty sure the logic I extracted is equivalent to what we were doing in all cases before.</p>\n</blockquote>",
